RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

97-1753. Disciplinary Counsel v. Zingarelli.

Reported at 81 Ohio St.3d 86, 689 N.E.2d 545. This cause came on for further consideration upon respondent’s motion for reconsideration and motion for stay. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motions be, and hereby are, denied.

Douglas, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., dissent.
